*William-Adolphe Bouguereau – 12 paintings including &quot;The Birth of Venus&quot;, &quot;La Danse&quot;, &quot;Dante and Virgil&quot;
*Louise Catherine Breslau - 4 paintings including &quot;Portrait of Henry Davison&quot;
