*André Derain – &quot;Charing Cross Bridge&quot;, also known as &quot;Westminster Bridge&quot;
*Édouard Detaille – &quot;The Dream&quot;
*Albert Edelfelt - &quot;Pasteur&#x27;s portrait by Edelfelt&quot;
