*Jean-Léon Gérôme – &quot;Portrait of the Baroness Nathaniel de Rothschild&quot;, &quot;Reception of Condé in Versailles&quot;, &quot;La Comtesse de Keller&quot;, &quot;The Cock Fight&quot;, &quot;Jerusalem&quot;
